properties.SQL select query:
SELECT p.PLPAGE_ID , p.ADMINNAME , sk.URLKEYWORD, p.STOREENT_ID, sc.value AS hostname  FROM seourl s, SEOURLKEYWORD sk, plpage p, STOREREL sr, storeconf sc
WHERE s.seourl_id = sk.SEOURL_ID 
AND s.TOKENVALUE =cast(p.PLPAGE_ID AS VARCHAR)
AND p.URLCONFIGURABLE = 1
AND sk.LANGUAGE_ID = -1
AND p.STOREENT_ID = sr.RELATEDSTORE_ID 
AND sk.STATUS = 1
AND sr.STORE_ID = ${param.storeId}
AND sr.STRELTYP_ID = -11
AND sr.STATE = 1
AND sc.STOREENT_ID = sr.STORE_ID 
AND sc.name='wc.search.indexcrawl.hostname';
